### SampleApp API - Admin Configuration/Settings Endpoints
### VSCode REST Client Extension: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client
### Uses variables from backend/.env (configured in .vscode/settings.json)
### Requires: Admin authentication

@contentType = application/json

### Get token from auth.rest login endpoint first
@token = your_jwt_token_here


### ===== CONFIGURATION MANAGEMENT =====

### List All Config Items
GET {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Config Items by Category
GET {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/config?category=general
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List All Categories
GET {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/config/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Config Grouped by Category
GET {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/config/by-category
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Single Config Item
GET {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/config/app_name
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Single Config Item
PUT {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/config/app_name
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "value": "{{$dotenv APP_NAME}}"
}

### Bulk Update Config Items
PUT {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "configs": {
        "app_name": "{{$dotenv APP_NAME}}",
        "support_email": "support@example.com",
        "maintenance_mode": "false"
    }
}

### Clear Cache and Seed Default Config
POST {{$dotenv API_URL}}/api/admin/config/clear-cache
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
